The '''''Chip''''' was a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] under the service of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. The ''Chip'' along with the Corvette Group ''[[Yogi]]'' and an [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|RZ-1 A-wing interceptor]] destroyed the [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighter]] group ''[[Sornsen]]'' and the Corvette group ''[[Shurik]]''.

